I'm bugfixing problems in the incoming-links macro at the moment and in my testing I have discovered that LinkManager.getIncomingLinksToContent does not return links that are stored in comments. It seems to work fine for links which are held in the body of pages or blogposts, but not from comments which are either attached to a page/blogpost that does contain a link, or those which do not contain a link within the body of the main CEO.

